0256|- [HelpText]
0257|*'Fixed' parameters for edit field control:
0259|*Max. number of columns on a line:
0260|*Parameter `ep4' has several related tasks. When the user activates Survo
0261|*operations, the system has to interpret edit lines consisting of several
0262|*words separated by spaces and commas. Also when reading tables written
0263|*in the edit field, the system must `see' the number of columns etc. In
0264|*many cases `ep4' is the maximum number of such words or numbers on one
0265|*edit line. In certain statistical analyses it will be the maximum number
0266|*of variables. Example: ep4=300 .
0268|*Max. lengths of lines and names:
0269|*Parameter `llength' (=1000) corresponds to the maximum line length in
0270|*edit fields. It cannot be changed by the user; the entire system must be
0271|*recompiled if this parameter is changed. Parameter `lname' (=256) has
0272|*also a fixed value in the same sense. It is the maximum allowed length
0273|*of a pathname in Survo functions.
